Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: aiida-siesta
Version: 1.1.1
Summary: A plugin for Siesta's basic functionality within the AiiDA framework.
Home-page: https://github.com/albgar/aiida_siesta_plugin
Author: Alberto Garcia, Victor M. Garcia-Suarez, Emanuele Bosoni, Vladimir Dikan, Pol Febrer
Author-email: albertog@icmab.es
License: MIT License
Description: AiiDA Siesta plugins and workflows
        ==================================
        
        A plugin to interface the `Siesta DFT code <https://icmab.es/siesta/>`_
        to the `AiiDA system <http://www.aiida.net/>`_.
        
        Documentation can be found in:
        
        http://aiida-siesta-plugin.readthedocs.io
        
        
